                        "id": "ir-3.3_gdn",
                        "name": "guidance",
                        "prose": "To help incident response activities function as intended, organizations may use metrics and evaluation criteria to assess incident response programs as part of an effort to continually improve response performance. These efforts facilitate improvement in incident response efficacy and lessen the impact of incidents."
